RAW FOOTAGE FROM THE BEDROOM?

36:17.370 --> 36:20.669
THE NIGHT THOSE GLOVES
LANDED IN DANNY'S CUBBYHOLE.

36:20.710 --> 36:22.803
- 'KAY.

36:25.880 --> 36:26.847
- HAN K?

36:26.880 --> 36:28.848
- THE CAMERA GUY?

36:28.880 --> 36:29.949
