IN CUSTODY.

36:29.980 --> 36:31.686
JAY DIDN'T SABOTAGE
HIS OWN SHOW.

36:31.720 --> 36:32.687
- WHERE'S HANK NOW?

36:32.720 --> 36:34.813
- HE'S ON LOCATION FILMING
MELINDA AND DANNY

36:34.860 --> 36:36.782
