36:36.820 --> 36:38.822
- HAN K?

36:41.700 --> 36:47.696
[siren]

36:57.340 --> 36:58.807
GUS!
- WHAT?

36:58.850 --> 36:59.748
- LET'S GO!

36:59.780 --> 37:04.240
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

37:04.290 --> 37:06.588
- SPENCER, WHERE THE HELL
ARE YOU GOING?

37:06.620 --> 37:07.587
- DANNY!

37:07.620 --> 37:09.713
- SHAWN!

37:09.760 --> 37:11.682
- DON'T TAKE
THAT LEAP!

37:11.730 --> 37:13.721
- NO, SHAWN, DON'T WORRY.
WE TALKED ABOUT IT.

37:13.760 --> 37:15.728
WE'RE READY FOR THIS!

37:15.760 --> 37:17.728
- YEAH! WE'RE IN LOVE.

37:17.760 --> 37:19.819
- YEAH!
- THANKS TO YOU, SHAWN.

37:19.870 --> 37:22.839
- NO, NO, NO,
NOT THAT LEAP.

37:22.870 --> 37:23.962
THE CHUTE,
IT'S NOT SAFE!

37:24.000 --> 37:24.967
- WHAT?

37:25.010 --> 37:26.830
- THE CHUTE!

37:26.870 --> 37:29.737
- YEAH! NO,
IT'S THE FINAL SHOOT.

37:29.780 --> 37:32.271
[whooping]

37:32.310 --> 37:34.847
- SHAWN, SHAWN,
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,

37:34.880 --> 37:38.418
BUT THE LAST TIME I CHECKED,
I WASN'T FASTER THAN A PLANE.

37:38.450 --> 37:40.748
- YOU KNOW, BUDDY,
IN RETROSPECT,

37:40.790 --> 37:41.814
