37:58.840 --> 37:59.807
PUT IT DOWN!

37:59.840 --> 38:03.571
GET OUT HERE.

38:03.610 --> 38:04.747
- HANK, I KNOW
YOU WERE THE ONE

38:04.780 --> 38:06.407
THAT HAD THE IDEA
FOR THIS SHOW FIRST.

38:06.450 --> 38:09.840
BUT YOURS WAS CALLED
PASSING SHIPS.

38:09.880 --> 38:10.869
AM I RIGHT?

38:10.920 --> 38:12.581
- YES.

38:12.620 --> 38:14.019
- A SHOW ABOUT
A FEMALE CONTESTANT

38:14.050 --> 38:15.654
WHO'S REINTRODUCED

38:15.690 --> 38:17.715
TO SUITORS FROM HER PAST
WHO SHE COULD HAVE MET

38:17.760 --> 38:19.352
BUT OVERLOOKED.

38:19.390 --> 38:20.652
- HOW DID YOU--

38:20.690 --> 38:22.624
- IT'S MY SKILL SET, JACK.

38:22.660 --> 38:24.059
YOU THOUGHT JAY WAS
GONNA MAKE YOU A PARTNER,

38:24.100 --> 38:26.898
BUT INSTEAD HE WENT OUT,
SOLD THIS THING WITHOUT YOU.

38:26.930 --> 38:29.091
HE WAS LYING,
BUT YOU DIDN'T KNOW THAT.

38:29.140 --> 38:31.631
WHEN JAY STARTED BRAGGING
ABOUT THE SHOW,

38:31.670 --> 38:33.865
YOU DECIDED YOU WERE
GONNA SABOTAGE THIS THING

38:33.910 --> 38:35.775
AT ALL COSTS TO MAKE SURE
IT WASN'T SUCCESSFUL.

38:35.810 --> 38:37.778
- HANK, STOP FILMING.

38:37.810 --> 38:40.574
WHAT ARE YOU DOING,
YOU IDIOT?

38:40.610 --> 38:43.773
- THAT'S COLD, HANK.
COLD-BLOODED, HANK.

38:43.820 --> 38:47.813
YOUR FINAL PLAN WAS TO SWITCH
OUT DANNY BOY'S CHUTE...

38:50.060 --> 38:51.459
WITH GUS' DIRTY LAUNDRY.

38:51.490 --> 38:52.582
- THAT'S NOT
MY LAUNDRY, SHAWN.

38:52.630 --> 38:53.619
- WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

38:53.660 --> 38:55.093
- THAT'S NOT
MY LAUNDRY.

38:55.130 --> 38:56.893
- YOU SAYING I'M HOLDING ON
TO SOME RANDOM DUDE'S DRAWERS?

38:56.930 --> 38:58.466
- I GUESS SO.

38:58.500 --> 39:00.764
YOU TWO WERE GONNA FALL
TO YOUR DEATHS.

39:00.800 --> 39:02.688
- [gaSPSJ
