39:05.640 --> 39:06.664
- I DON'T--I DON'T KNOW.

39:06.710 --> 39:07.768
- TAKE 'EM.

39:07.810 --> 39:08.777
- NO.
- TAKE THESE!

39:08.810 --> 39:09.731
- I DON'T WANT THEM, SHAWN.

39:09.780 --> 39:10.769
- TAKE THESE DRAWERS!

39:10.810 --> 39:12.778
- I AIN'T GONNA TAKE THEM.

39:12.810 --> 39:14.346
- TAKE 'EM!
