I AIN'T GETTIN'
ON NO ROCKET.

39:32.900 --> 39:34.128
NOW THOSE OF YOU WHO CAUGHT
THE LAST EPISODE,

39:34.170 --> 39:36.092
YOU KNOW THAT SHAWN HAD A HAND
IN PLAYING CUPID.

39:36.140 --> 39:38.802
- OH, WHAT CAN I SAY?

39:38.840 --> 39:40.432
I LOVE MAKING LOVE.

39:42.140 --> 39:44.074
I HAD A FANTASTIC TIME
ON THE SHOW.

39:44.110 --> 39:46.078
- NOW THAT WASN'T
ALWAYS THE CASE.

39:46.110 --> 39:50.046
