39:50.080 --> 39:51.718
- WHAT THE EFF?

39:51.750 --> 39:54.958
HEY, GUYS, COME ON.

39:54.990 --> 39:57.652
WHO DOESN'T PUT THE LID
ON THE ICE CREAM BACK?

39:57.690 --> 39:58.952
LOOK AT THIS,
WHAT IS THIS?

39:58.990 --> 39:59.957
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT IS?
THAT'S FREEZER BURN.

39:59.990 --> 40:01.753
WE'RE BACHELORS,

40:01.800 --> 40:02.994
IT DOESN'T MEAN THAT
WE'RE LIVING ALONE.

40:03.030 --> 40:05.590
THE FIRST THOUGHT THAT I HAD
WHEN I WALKED DOWN THOSE STAIRS

40:05.630 --> 40:07.518
AND SAW MELINDA
STANDING THERE,

40:07.570 --> 40:11.028
UM, IN THAT RUFFLY
DRESS, WAS, UM,

40:11.070 --> 40:13.061
"NOT BAD FOR A STAND-IN.

