- [nervous laughter]

41:14.030 --> 41:16.089
- YOUR CALL.

41:16.140 --> 41:17.892
- WOW.

41:17.940 --> 41:18.907
- IS THIS A JOKE?

41:18.940 --> 41:20.066
- COME BACK OVER HERE.

41:20.110 --> 41:21.008
HAVE SOME MORE LEMONADE.

41:21.040 --> 41:22.007
- I DON'T WANT ANY LEMONADE!

41:22.040 --> 41:24.873
[laughter]

41:24.910 --> 41:27.845
- WOW, WELL, THAT IS
A PATHS OF LOVE FIRST.

41:27.880 --> 41:30.041
WE'VE NOW SAVED
THE BEST FOR LAST.

41:30.080 --> 41:32.116
DANNY...

41:32.150 --> 41:34.289
IT'S HIGHLY UNLIKELY THAT YOU
WOULD BE SITTING IN THAT CHAIR

41:34.320 --> 41:36.618
IF NOT FOR THE TWO-MONTH
MEDICALLY-INDUCED COMA

41:36.660 --> 41:38.525
OF THIS GENTLEMAN.

41:38.560 --> 41:41.996
BACHELORS, PUT YOUR HANDS
TOGETHER FOR TODD KRAMER.

41:42.030 --> 41:43.998
ALIVE AND WELL.

41:44.030 --> 41:49.036
[applause and cheering]

41:54.010 --> 41:55.898
- HEY.
- WOW.

